---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AnalysisSequence from '../components/AnalysisSequence.astro';
import RoleIssueCrosswalk from '../components/RoleIssueCrosswalk.astro';
import { analysisStages } from '../data/analysis';
---

<BaseLayout title="Analysis map" description="A six-stage method for testing a dealership pay system without collapsing facts, classifications, calculations, legal routes, and proof into one conclusion.">
  <main id="main-content">
    <header class="map-hero shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Analytical operating system · version 1.0</p>
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <h1>One sequence.<br /><span>Six distinct jobs.</span></h1>
        <div>
          <p class="lede">A reliable review moves from facts to action without letting a pay label, one record, or one exemption answer a different question.</p>
          <p class="scope">California + federal · source checked 2026-07-18</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <AnalysisSequence />
    </header>

    <section class="section shell stage-manual" aria-labelledby="manual-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div><p class="eyebrow">The decision sequence</p><h2 id="manual-title">Keep each inference in its lane.</h2></div>
        <p>Each stage has a different object, evidence burden, and failure mode. Skipping one does not save work; it hides an assumption inside a conclusion.</p>
      </div>
      <ol>
        {analysisStages.map((stage) => (
          <li id={stage.id}>
            <div class="stage-id"><span>{stage.number}</span><strong>{stage.label}</strong></div>
            <div class="stage-question"><p class="data-label">Controlling question</p><h3>{stage.question}</h3><p>{stage.description}</p></div>
            <div class="stage-control"><p class="data-label">Analytical control</p><p>{stage.prevents}</p></div>
            <div class="stage-records"><p class="data-label">Working record set</p><ul>{stage.records.map((record) => <li>{record}</li>)}</ul></div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--mist"><div class="shell"><RoleIssueCrosswalk /></div></section>

    <section class="section shell closing-test">
      <p class="eyebrow">Output standard</p>
      <h2>The defensible output is a bounded next step.</h2>
      <div>
        <p>State the proposition being tested, the facts that select it, the period and unit of measurement, the supporting and contradictory records, the unresolved predicate, and the action owner.</p>
        <p>Do not convert incomplete inputs into a risk score, compliance verdict, liability finding, or claim valuation. Precision includes saying what the present record cannot decide.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .map-hero { padding-block: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem); }
  .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2fr) minmax(17rem, 1fr); gap: var(--space-7); align-items: end; margin-bottom: var(--space-7); }
  h1 { margin-bottom: 0; }
  h1 span { color: var(--color-cobalt); }
  .hero-grid p { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .scope { margin-top: 1rem !important; color: var(--color-muted); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .stage-manual > ol { margin: 0; padding: 0; border-top: 4px solid var(--color-ink); list-style: none; }
  .stage-manual > ol > li { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 8rem minmax(13rem, 1.3fr) minmax(12rem, 1fr) minmax(12rem, 1fr); gap: var(--space-5); border-bottom: var(--rule); padding-block: 1.6rem; scroll-margin-top: 2rem; }
  .stage-id { display: grid; align-content: start; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .stage-id span { color: var(--color-cobalt); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; }
  .stage-id strong { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.35rem; }
  .stage-question h3 { margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
  .stage-question > p:last-child,
  .stage-control > p:last-child { margin: 0; font-size: 0.91rem; }
  .stage-records ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1rem; }
  .stage-records li { font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .data-label { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .closing-test { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 9rem minmax(16rem, 1.4fr) minmax(16rem, 1fr); gap: var(--space-6); border-top: 4px solid var(--color-ink); }
  .closing-test h2,
  .closing-test p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .closing-test div p { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  @media (max-width: 66rem) { .stage-manual > ol > li { grid-template-columns: 7rem 1fr 1fr; } .stage-records { grid-column: 2 / -1; } }
  @media (max-width: 48rem) { .hero-grid, .closing-test { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .stage-manual > ol > li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .stage-records { grid-column: auto; } }
</style>
